~ start
if not DMM.get_temp("Boss_talk_L1")
	*Cough cough
	Good to see you alive, soldier!
	We need you to quick reconenance. One of our fallen brothers has card to open this doors.
	Take one of the repellents; I don't have many left, so I'll stay here and cover the exit.
	do DMM.receive_item("Repellent", 1)
	do DMM.add_temp("Boss_talk_L1")
else
	Move your ass and bring that card, quickly!
